headline: Meet the High-Tech Construction Stock That's Already a 100-Bagger and Is Poised To Beat the Market in 2025
summary: If you're looking for high-powered growth stocks, you're first instinct is probably to look in the tech sector.  The company calls itself a global climate innovator, and climate change and related demographic trends have been a meaningful tailwind for the company.  Heading into 2025, Trane Technologies looks poised to continue beating the market.
